text: Sangowal may refer to: *Sangowal is a village in Kapurthala district of Punjab State *Sangowal (Ludhiana West) is a village located in the Ludhiana West tehsil, of Ludhiana district, Punjab. *Feroz Sangowal is a village in Bhulath Tehsil in Kapurthala district of Punjab State, India.
title: Sangowal (disambiguation)
